track_notes: The easiest approach from the Top Car Park. Note that this car park is pay and display.
A straight forward walk from the Car Park.Although you should stick to the wide track and not take the narrow path on the right as I did on the way up.
Easy walk, ideal for families. Nice views in clear weather.

Total time (including ops): 1hr 20m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
